headline: 30 Duke Energy lineworkers from across Carolinas secure spots to compete at International Lineman's Rodeo this fall
summary: The air was electric, and the energy was tangible at a competition over the weekend where 30 Duke Energy lineworkers from across North Carolina and South Carolina took home top awards at the Carolinas Lineman's Rodeo – earning the opportunity to move on to one of the most prominent and celebrated lineworker events in the world.
